<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Terri Irwin is expecting her first grandchild in 2021. </p>

<p>And the Australia Zoo matriarch, 56, spoke proudly of her pregnant daughter Bindi, 22, in a tweet shared on Sunday.</p>

<p>She posted a photo of herself with her arm around her beaming daughter to mark National Daughter Day.</p>

<p>'She is the most wonderful person': Terri Irwin (left) paid tribute to her pregnant daughter Bindi, 22, on Sunday</p>

<p>'I know <?php echo e('@'); ?>BindiIrwin will be an amazing mother, because she is the most wonderful daughter in the world,' Terri wrote.</p>

<p>'She always gives me the best advice. Most recently, she said to me, "Be sure to revel in your achievements, and not just worry about your next challenge." </p>

<p>Last week, Bindi and her husband, Chandler Powell, revealed they were expecting a daughter in a sweet gender reveal.</p>

<p>It's a girl: Last week, Bindi and her husband Chandler Powell revealed they are expecting a daughter who is 'as healthy as can be'. She shared a photo of herself cuddled up to an Aldabra tortoise at her home in Australia Zoo, Queensland to Instagram</p>

<p>The mother-to-be, 22, shared a photo to Instagram of herself cuddled up to an Aldabra tortoise at Australia Zoo. </p>

<p>Bindi wrote in the caption: 'Baby girl, you are our world.</p>

<p>'Our beautiful daughter is now about the same size as a hatchling Aldabra tortoise and is as healthy as can be.</p>

<p>Baby makes three: Bindi and Chandler revealed their baby news last month on Instagram, with the pair holding up a baby sized Australia Zoo khaki uniform. 'Baby Wildlife Warrior due 2021,' she excitedly announced in the caption</p>

<p>'We can't wait for her arrival next year,' the wildlife warrior added.</p>

<p>Chandler also shared the same sweet photo, and wrote in the caption: 'Our little girl and my beautiful wife are my entire world.</p>

<p>'I'm so excited to meet our daughter when she’s born next year and to see the incredible person she will grow up to be ❤️.'</p>

<p>Just married! The young couple were married on March 25, in a makeshift ceremony at Australia Zoo, just before Covid pandemic lockdown</p>

<p>The couple revealed their baby news last month, sharing a photo to Instagram of themselves holding up a baby-sized Australia Zoo uniform.</p>

<p>'Baby Wildlife Warrior due 2021,' Bindi excitedly announced in the caption.</p>

<p>The young lovebirds married on March 25 at a small ceremony at Australia Zoo, after the COVID-19 pandemic forced them to cancel their original plans.</p>

<p>They met close to seven years ago, in November 2013, when Chandler, who hails from Florida, was touring Australia for a wakeboarding competition.</p>

<p>First love: The couple met close to seven years ago in November 2013 when Chandler, who hails from Florida, was touring Australia for a wakeboarding competition</p>
